  "text": "In this paper, in accordance with [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] , we focus on a specific version of the binary similarity problem in which we define two binary functions to be similar if they are compiled from the same source code. As already pointed out in [CITATION_3] , this assumption does not make the problem trivial.",
